{"id":5,"category_slug":"short-stories","category_name":"Short Stories","position":2,"title":"2. Jessica's first day of school","subtitle":"","level":"A1","parts":25,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/short-stories/2-jessicas-first-day-of-school.5/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/2-jessicas-first-day-of-school-2019-03-15-00-20-34/0-2-jessicas-first-day-of-school.mp3","transcript":"Today is Jessica's first day of kindergarten.\nJessica and her parents walk to school.\nJessica's mom walks with her to her classroom.\nJessica meets her teacher.\nHis name is Mr. Parker.\nThe school bell rings at 8:45 a.m.\nJessica hugs and kisses her mom goodbye.\nJessica's mom says \"I love you!\".\nAt 9 a.m, Jessica stands for the national anthem.\nMr. Parker calls out children's names.\nEach child yells back \"here!\".\nMr. Parker teaches them about letters.\nMr. Parker teaches them about numbers.\nAt 10:15 a.m, the students have recess.\nRecess is fun.\nThe students get to play and eat.\nAt 10:30 a.m.\nthe students go to gym class.\nAt 11:15 a.m.\nthe students return to Mr. Parker's classroom.\nMr. Parker tells the students to sit on the carpet.\nMr. Parker reads the students a story.\nMr. Parker teaches the students a song.\nThe lunch bell rings.\nJessica's first day of school is over.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:35:25","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Today is Jessica's first day of kindergarten.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/2-jessicas-first-day-of-school-2019-03-15-00-20-34/1.mp3","time_start":4.4,"time_end":7.9},{"position":2,"content":"Jessica and her parents walk to school.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/2-jessicas-first-day-of-school-2019-03-15-00-20-34/2.mp3","time_start":8.8,"time_end":11.6},{"position":3,"content":"Jessica's mom walks with her to her classroom.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-